    {
      "id": "25f67c25-1a01-4f96-94e5-c591008b8ff9",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $a_1,\\dots,a_n \\in  K$ distincts et $P = (X-a_1)\\dots(X-a_n)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_1,\\dots,a_n \\in  K\\)</span> distincts et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P = (X-a_1)\\dots(X-a_n)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e8e6e0a6-8709-4fbf-b150-ba21b8b11fb0",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}composer en {\\'e}l{\\'e}ments simples la fraction $\\frac {(1+X^2)^n}{P^2}$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>composer en <span>é</span>l<span>é</span>ments simples la fraction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {(1+X^2)^n}{P^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "94e9b48f-403a-4880-8da0-6a45bd29f946",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que les coefficients des $\\frac1{X-a_i}$ sont tous nuls si et seulement si :\n    $(1+X^2)P'' - 2nXP' + n(n+1)P = 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que les coefficients des <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac1{X-a_i}\\)</span> sont tous nuls si et seulement si : <span class=\"math inline\">\\((1+X^2)P&#39;&#39; - 2nXP&#39; + n(n+1)P = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6bc50645-b072-4531-accd-a59d2c3f4fb3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_{i=1}^n \\Bigl( \\frac{(1+a_i^2)^n}{P'^2(a_i)(X-a_i)^2}\n             + \\frac{2na_i - P''(a_i)(1+a_i^2)/P'(a_i)}{P'^2(a_i)(X-a_i)} \\Bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{i=1}^n \\Bigl( \\frac{(1+a_i^2)^n}{P&#39;^2(a_i)(X-a_i)^2}\n             + \\frac{2na_i - P&#39;&#39;(a_i)(1+a_i^2)/P&#39;(a_i)}{P&#39;^2(a_i)(X-a_i)} \\Bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
